snippet.title: The Dark Pictures: Man of Medan - PS4 / Xbox1 / PC - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
SUPERMASSIVE Games and Bandai Namco Entertainment are partnering up to bring you the first ever horror anthology series - The Dark Pictures.

Today, we'll introduce you to the first episode of the series: Man Of Medan.
